description: A video of Kamala Harris taking a voter phone call went viral after some social media users said she ‘mistakenly’ showed her phone was open on the camera app.   But this has now been 'debunked' with some Trump supporters pointing out that you can in fact stay on a call while using the camera.  #harris #kamalaharris #uselection #phonecall
